      "description": "Particle image velocimetry measurements at 5 flow-speed combinations compared against CFD velocity fields. Mean absolute error < 8 % across all planes. Uncertainty quantification performed via Monte Carlo propagation of inlet boundary condition variability (N=5000 samples).",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": {
