      "name": "Pump pressure-rise validation across speed sweep",
      "description": "Predicted hydraulic head compared with bench measurements across 2000–3500 RPM at 4 L/min and 6 L/min. Agreement within 4 % at all tested conditions. Uncertainty quantification performed via Latin hypercube sampling of fluid viscosity and rotational speed tolerance.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": {
